"learning is presumably making the participants less active. However, direct "
"learning can still be used together with question and answer, "
"demonstrations, and exercises. Furthermore, a few ways can be used to make "
"more this method more effective, for example:"
msgstr ""
"Pembelajaran langsung biasanya diidentikkan dengan metode ceramah, dimana "
"pembelajaran ini disinyalir kurang mengaktifkan peserta. Namun demikian "
"pembelajaran langsung masih dapat digunakan dengan menggunakan metode "
"tanyajawab, demonstrasi, dan latihan. Selanjutnya dapat digunakan beberapa "
