# 3a58cddc9f334b1595f73bfa5bd74469
#: ../../source/training/tot/502_communication_skills.rst:777
msgid ""
"This reinforcement may be in the form of asking participants to help his "
"friends when he has finished his work properly, participants are asked to "
"lead activities, etc."
msgstr ""
"Penguatan ini dapat berupa meminta peserta membantu temannya bila dia "
